# Import libraries 
import re 
import requests

# Function to check for SQL injection
def check_sqli_vulnerability (url) : 
    # Regular expression
    regex = re.compile('(AND\s|OR\s)(\d+?=\d+?|"\w+?"="\w+?"|\'\w+?\'=\'\w+?\')')

    # Send a Get request    
    response = requests.get(url)
    data = response.text
    weakness = re.findall(regex, data)

    # Check if there are vulnerable expressions    
    if len(list(weakness)) > 0 : 
        print('SQL injection vulnerability detected!')

# Function to check for XSS vulnerability
def check_xss_vulnerability(url):
    # Regular Expression to detect xss vulnerabilities
    p = re.compile('<script.*?>.*?<\/script>')
    
    # Send a Get request    
    response = requests.get(url)
    data = response.text
    vulnerability = re.findall(p, data)
    
    # Check if there are vulnerable expressions
    if len(list(vulnerability)) > 0 :
        print('XSS vulnerability detected!')
       
url = 'http://www.example.com/check-vulnerabilities.php'
check_sqli_vulnerability(url)
check_xss_vulnerability(url)
